OL,7,FA plan for funding and retiring the
OL,8,FUK's gas network is "desperately
OL,9,Fneeded" as the country shifts towards
OL,10,Fclean energy, experts have said.
OL,12,FThe UK Energy Research Centre (UKERC)
OL,13,Fhas backed the Government's mission to
OL,14,Fachieve clean power by 2030, which
OL,15,FLabour said last week would mean at
OL,16,Fleast 95% low-carbon electricity by
OL,17,Fthe end of the decade.
