OL,7,FBut in its annual review of energy
OL,8,Fpolicy, UKERC warned clean power by
OL,9,F2030 is just a first step towards a
OL,10,Fwider vision of clean energy `
OL,11,Fincluding for heating and industry `
OL,12,Fin the 2030s and beyond.
OL,14,FThe researchers said gas
OL,15,Finfrastructure will remain key to
OL,16,Fenergy security for the coming years,
OL,17,Fbut faces decline as Britain moves to
OL,18,Frenewable power and clean home heating
OL,19,Fsystems to cut greenhouse gas
OL,20,Femissions to zero overall by 2050.
