OL,7,FIt could cost as much as #29 billion
OL,8,Fto disconnect customers from the gas
OL,9,Fnetwork and #25 billion to physically
OL,10,Fdecommission the pipelines, the report
OL,11,Fwarned.
OL,13,FA "whole system plan for the
OL,14,Fretirement of the network is
OL,15,Fdesperately needed" with decisions on
OL,16,Fthe technology mix for home heating,
OL,17,Fclarity on boiler phase-out dates, the
OL,18,Frole of hydrogen, and even potential
OL,19,Fnationalisation of the network, a
OL,20,Freport from the research centre said.
