OL,7,FUKERC warned it is essential to
OL,8,Faddress how gas infrastructure will be
OL,9,Ffunded in future, and to carefully and
OL,10,Fstrategically plan the transition away
OL,11,Ffrom the fossil fuel.
OL,13,FThe report also said the challenge of
OL,14,Fmeeting the 2030 goal should not
OL,15,Fdistract from the even larger
OL,16,Fchallenges of the following decades,
OL,17,Fwhen the whole power system needs to
OL,18,Fexpand as people switch to electric
OL,19,Fheating and cars and new
OL,20,Finfrastructure will be needed.
