OL,7,FIt called for measures to ensure the
OL,8,Fenergy transition delivers for
OL,9,Fvulnerable consumers faced with high
OL,10,Ffuel prices, with adequate funding for
OL,11,Fthe Government's warm homes plan,
OL,12,Fdelivery of insulation and reforms to
OL,13,Fthe electricity market to deliver
OL,14,Faffordable energy for lower income
OL,15,Fhouseholds.
