OL,7,FAnd with half of industrial energy
OL,8,Fconsumption still provided by fossil
OL,9,Ffuels, an industrial strategy with a
OL,10,Fstrong focus on decarbonisation is
OL,11,Fneeded, and protection of nature
OL,12,Fshould be at the heart of the energy
OL,13,Ftransition, it said.
OL,15,FProfessor Robert Gross, director of
OL,16,FUKERC, said: "The clean power mission
OL,17,Fis a bold and commendable step that is
OL,18,Fpart of a larger, long-term vision for
OL,19,Fsustainable and affordable home-grown
OL,20,Fenergy, based largely on the UK's
OL,21,Ffantastic renewable resources.
