OL,7,F"The 2030 target is one milestone on
OL,8,Fthe road to achieving the UK's
OL,9,Fcommitment to an 81% reduction in
OL,10,Fgreenhouse gas emissions by 2035, and
OL,11,Fnet zero 2050.
OL,13,F"Achieving this will require co-
OL,14,Fordinated efforts across the entire
OL,15,Fenergy system."
OL,17,FDr Jess Britton, co-director of UKERC,
OL,18,Fadded: "The energy transition must not
OL,19,Fleave anyone behind.
